name: 李老师不是你老师
content:
February 9, Taiyuan, Shanxi. Owners of the unfinished building of Taihe Jinzunfu posted couplets outside the developer's door.
One of the couplets reads "Five thousand owners of unfinished buildings of Taihe across the country have collectively stopped paying their mortgages. You have worked hard for half your life to buy a house at Taihe, but now you have lost everything in one day."
It is understood that the building has been unfinished for five years.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: Spring Festival Gala episode: During a language show that night, a group of crosstalk performers wore rainbow-colored clothes, which was ridiculed by netizens as "Spring Festival Gala speaks for LGBT", and the related topic was subsequently banned

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: On February 9, a video of the "I Love Going to Work" program performed by Shandong Nuclear Power Employees at their 2024 Party went viral online, sparking heated discussion.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content:
On February 9, in Xiaogan, Hubei, an old man clashed with the urban management staff for selling Spring Festival couplets at a stall, and was knocked down and pinned down by a group of urban management staff.
At the end of the video, the old man was dying and did not move.

name: 李老师不是你老师
